                    <div class="feature-icon">üì±</div>
                    <h3 class="feature-title">No Programming</h3>
                    <p class="feature-desc">
                        Configure everything via mobile app. Zero coding
                        knowledge required.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-icon">üîå</div>
                    <h3 class="feature-title">Universal Sensors</h3>
                    <p class="feature-desc">
                        Supports 95% of market sensors: 4-20mA, 0-10V, RS485,
                        IIC
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-icon">üåê</div>
                    <h3 class="feature-title">Remote Control</h3>
