                        reliable remote access.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-icon">‚ö°</div>
                    <h3 class="feature-title">Instant Deploy</h3>
                    <p class="feature-desc">
                        10x simpler than traditional PLC. Production-ready in
                        one day.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Product Showcase -->
